      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（星見市でご当地PRイベントが開催され）\n（トークイベントにさくらが登壇することになっていた）",
      "startTime": 3.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "……という訳なので、ぜひみなさんも\n星見市の魅力に気付いてもらえたら……",
      "startTime": 11.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そして、私達サニーピースの魅力にも！\n気付いてもらえたら嬉しいです！",
      "startTime": 17.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-out-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 17.764810859795773
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "以上、サニーピース川咲さくらの\n星見市自慢トークでした！",
      "startTime": 23.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshistage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-host001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん、ありがとうございました～！\nでは、次のコーナーに参りましょう！",
      "startTime": 27.928313907950816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-host002.m4a",
      "text": "なんと、スペシャルゲストが来てくれています！\n星見市のマスコットキャラ『魚魚っとさん』でーす！",
      "startTime": 37.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（登場したのは、星見市のマスコットキャラで）\n（ブサイクな見た目で有名な『魚魚っとさん』だ）",
      "startTime": 43.64281701535701,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ぎょ……魚魚っとさんだ～！\n初めて本物に出会えました～！",
      "startTime": 49.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "すっごく好きなんです私！\nやったー、共演出来た！　夢みたいです！！",
      "startTime": 54.444768925305304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、見て下さい\nこのぎょろっとした目……",
      "startTime": 60.79476904451461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "どこ見てるか分からない感じが\nすっごく可愛いんですよー！",
      "startTime": 65.53762618737176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-host003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなんですね……！\n意外……ですねぇ……あはは",
      "startTime": 71.03545857042161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-host004.m4a",
      "text": "ち、ちなみに星見テレビで魚魚っとさんのアニメ化が\n決定したそうでして、今回はそのPRに……",
      "startTime": 78.6354585704216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　アニメ化！？　ぜ、絶対観ます！\nいつ放送するんですか？　私、楽しみです！！",
      "startTime": 86,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-host005.m4a",
      "text": "す、凄いですね……魚魚っとさんへの愛が炸裂してます\n他にどういった所が好き……とかあるんですか？",
      "startTime": 95.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　例えば背びれの曲線美とか\nひれの色とか……",
      "startTime": 102.13119833899133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（意外な一面を見せることが出来たのは良かったけど）\n（あまりの熱狂ぶりに時間が押してしまったな……）",
      "startTime": 109.79786500565794,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3614.8681810746552,
          "startTime": 113.4127331867326
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、{user}さん！\n私、ちょっとテンション上がり過ぎちゃって……",
      "startTime": 115.47939985339931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "「締めて！」ってカンペにも全然気付かなくって……\n迷惑かけちゃいましたよね？",
      "startTime": 122.97619435856154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "お客さんも楽しんでくれたみたいだし\n大丈夫だったと思うけど……次からは気を付けよう",
      "startTime": 128.21390526664374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "はい……そうですよね\n気を付けます",
      "startTime": 135.8629185091704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても意外だったな\nさくらが魚魚っとさんのファンだったなんて",
      "startTime": 139.60410436593847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか？\nそんなに変なのかな……",
      "startTime": 144.84047614596784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "サニピのみんなも、グッズを見せるとちょっと\n引いてる感じがあって……なんでなんだろう？",
      "startTime": 150.56821745675663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "趣味は人それぞれだし、変ではないよ。それに、まぁ\nよく見れば愛嬌がある……ように見える気もするしな",
      "startTime": 158.77878660896832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり{user}さんは\n分かってくれた……えへへ！",
      "startTime": 166.34545327563498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、一個グッズを分けてあげますね\nじっくり観察してみて下さい。魅力に気付くはずです！",
      "startTime": 172.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがとう……\nちなみに、いつ頃から集め始めたんだ？",
      "startTime": 178.7482390489462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "実は、あんまり覚えてないんですよね\nお母さん、お見舞いのたびに持って来てくれたから……",
      "startTime": 185.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "魚魚っとさんが、身近にいるのが当たり前だったんです\n入院生活も一緒に乗り越えてくれたし……",
      "startTime": 193.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_01_02-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか愛着も湧いてきちゃって……\nだから好きなんだと思います、魚魚っとさん",
      "startTime": 199.47358367394304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_stagesleeves"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
